n each level available, and you can climb almost anything anywhere\n- Destroy robots and dinosaurs\n- Motion Sickness Consideration: all horizontal turning can be done using the right joystick in addition to the direction you are looking, while flying move in direction of hand/jetpack.\n*Additional 5/23/2022 updates: major game mechanics improvements, new random level selector, level end-scenes with score and animal viewing, added multiple songs, added new animal spawns / animations and some random spawns*", "short_description": "-Zany ZOSULand Experience:\n-Climb, fly, grapple over 10 miles / 28 kilometers of futuristic urban areas to save each floating city and the multitude of animals\n- 27 unique city levels + 9 bonus levels\n- Over 250 building types to explore, over 40 types of animals to save\n- Jetpacks allow flight, grapples in each level available, climb almost anything anywhere\n- Destroy robots and dinosaurs"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "publisher_name": "ZOSU Studios LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.zosustudios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_FEW", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "388572352490011"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "DINOSAURS", "FLYING"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "82816437